<p>The whole idea of the informal grid is that we set one page element after another, starting with the most important. So letâ€™s set the title.</p>

<p>These are some variables you can work with:</p>

<ul class="hasBullets columns3">
	<li>size</li>
	<li>weight</li>
	<li>width</li>
	<li>case</li>
	<li>greys</li>
	<li>strokes</li>
	<li>columns</li>
	<li>diagonal</li>
	<li>italics</li>
	<li>reversed</li>
	<li>tracking</li>
</ul>

<p>Now weâ€™ll set the sub-title. It needs to appear noticeably less important than the title. Alignment is important here. Thatâ€™s the informal grid at work.</p>

<p>The last item is the block of body copy. Make sure to set proper leading and reasonable hyphenation.</p>

